pullRequest.body:
This PR introduces the very basic definitions of Mayer-Vietoris squares. It shall be expanded in future PRs towards the construction of Mayer-Vietoris long exact sequences in sheaf cohomology.

---

- [x] depends on: #14969
- [x] depends on: #14971
